#

Mushroom Flatbread

25 min
$8.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianQuick Meal

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodAppetizer

Description

Savory flatbread topped with sautéed mushrooms and melted cheese, perfect for a quick and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • flatbread: 2 pieces
  • mushrooms: 1 cup, sliced
  • mozzarella cheese: 1 cup, shredded
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
